(B_\varepsilon(0)+K)\subset\Omega
N=1
\Omega=(a,b)
K=[c,d]
\varepsilon<\min\{b-d,c-a\}
\begin{align*}x\in(B_\varepsilon(0)+K)&\Rightarrow x=y+z\text{ with }y\in (-\varepsilon,\varepsilon)\text{ and }z\in[c,d]\\ &\Rightarrow-\varepsilon+c < x<\varepsilon+d\\ &\Rightarrow a < x<b\\ &\Rightarrow x\in \Omega \end{align*}
